title: Refrigerator Power Cord
description: Refrigerator Power Cord PartSelect Number PS11732736 Manufacturer Part Number 3903-001003 This is a power cord made for Samsung refrigerators. If your current power cord is damaged, broken, or no longer supplying power to your fridge, you can disconnect it from the wall outlet, strip it from your fridge, and replace it with this OEM cord. This power cord is sold individually and does not include any other parts or accessories.
